
set the env and run the daphne server:
export DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE=realTimeMessaging.settings
daphne -b 0.0.0.0 -p 8000 realTimeMessaging.asgi:application

running redis service:
sudo service redis-server start
sudo service redis-server status

checking the ip of WSL (not needed if backend is running on WSL)
ip addr | grep inet -> look for the global ip address

Force and check the path:
hash -r
echo $PATH